<h2>Create a Company</h2>

<ol>
    <li>Click <em>Companies</em> on the left sidebar.</li>
    <li>Click the <em>Add Company</em> button on the top right.</li>
    <li>Enter the company name.</li>
    <li>Click <em>Choose File</em> and find the desired company logo.</li>
    <li>Click <em>Submit</em> and the company will be created!</li>
</ol>

